  <brief_title>An Open-Label Treatment Protocol With UX003 rhGUS Enzyme Replacement Therapy for an Advanced Stage MPS 7 Patient</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-Label Treatment Protocol With UX003 Recombinant Human Beta-glucuronidase (rhGUS) Enzyme Replacement Therapy for an Advanced Stage Mucopolysaccharidosis Type 7 (MPS 7) Patient</official_title>
