  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Emergency access granted to treat a single patient with advanced Mucopolysaccharidosis Type 7
      with UX003 Recombinant Human Beta-glucuronidase (rhGUS) Enzyme Replacement Therapy via IV
      administration every other week (QOW) for up to 144 weeks.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
